column2: select R.REF_1_RECORD, R.REF_1_AMT, R.REF_2_RECORD, R.REF_2_AMT, R.REF_1_M_REF_2_RECORD, R.REF_1_M_REF_2_AMT, R.REF_1_L_REF_2_RECORD, R.REF_1_L_REF_2_AMT, R.DIFF_BOO from PMDB..PM_PREPAID_BATCH_RECONCILE R inner join PMDB..PM_PREPAID_LOAD_BATCH B on (R.BATCH_ID = B.BATCH_ID) inner join PMDB..PM_RECONCILE_MAPPING M on (R.RECONCILE_ID = M.RECONCILE_ID)  where B.ORDER_ID = @order_id
